    About Fables & Fairy Tales

    Fables and Fairy Tales is a whimsical bookstore for the child in all of us. A magical place where imagination and adventure come to life. Our family owned and operated bookshop is located on the historic downtown square in Martinsville, IN. Our mission is to provide excellence in our products and services to our customers and local community. We offer a wide variety of books, toys and handcrafted items.
